---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
const updated = '2026-05-23';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Privacy Policy — GoinAtlas"
  description="Privacy policy for GoinAtlas. How we collect, use, and protect your data."
>
  <div class="max-w-2xl mx-auto px-6 py-16">
    <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-2" style="font-family: var(--font-display);">Privacy Policy</h1>
    <p class="text-sm text-[var(--color-text-muted)] mb-10">Last updated: {updated}</p>

    <div class="space-y-8 text-[var(--color-text-secondary)] leading-relaxed">

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-lg font-bold text-[var(--color-text-primary)] mb-3" style="font-family: var(--font-display);">1. What we collect</h2>
        <p>GoinAtlas collects limited data to operate the site:</p>
        <ul class="list-disc list-inside mt-2 space-y-1">
          <li><strong>Analytics:</strong> We use Google Analytics 4 to understand how visitors use the site (pages viewed, time on site, device type). This data is anonymized and aggregated.</li>
          <li><strong>Advertising:</strong> We use Google AdSense to display ads. Google may use cookies to serve personalized ads based on your browsing history.</li>
          <li><strong>Affiliate links:</strong> Some links are affiliate links (Travelpayouts, Aviasales, Hotellook). Clicking them may set a tracking cookie on the affiliate's site — not ours.</li>
          <li><strong>Newsletter:</strong> If you subscribe to our newsletter via Beehiiv, your email address is stored by Beehiiv under their privacy policy.</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-lg font-bold text-[var(--color-text-primary)] mb-3" style="font-family: var(--font-display);">2. Cookies</h2>
        <p>We use cookies for:</p>
        <ul class="list-disc list-inside mt-2 space-y-1">
          <li>Site preferences (e.g. sidebar state, reading list) — stored locally in your browser</li>
          <li>Google Analytics — measures site traffic</li>
          <li>Google AdSense — may serve personalized ads</li>
        </ul>
        <p class="mt-3">You can disable cookies in your browser settings at any time.</p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-lg font-bold text-[var(--color-text-primary)] mb-3" style="font-family: var(--font-display);">3. Third-party services</h2>
        <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-1">
          <li><a href="https://policies.google.com/privacy" class="text-[var(--color-brand-600)] hover:underline" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Google Analytics Privacy Policy</a></li>
          <li><a href="https://policies.google.com/technologies/ads" class="text-[var(--color-brand-600)] hover:underline" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Google AdSense & Advertising</a></li>
          <li><a href="https://travelpayouts.com/en/privacy" class="text-[var(--color-brand-600)] hover:underline" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Travelpayouts Privacy Policy</a></li>
          <li><a href="https://www.beehiiv.com/privacy" class="text-[var(--color-brand-600)] hover:underline" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Beehiiv Privacy Policy</a></li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-lg font-bold text-[var(--color-text-primary)] mb-3" style="font-family: var(--font-display);">4. Your rights</h2>
        <p>Depending on your location, you may have rights to access, correct, or delete personal data we hold about you. Contact us at <a href="mailto:hello@goinatlas.com" class="text-[var(--color-brand-600)] hover:underline">hello@goinatlas.com</a> for any data requests.</p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-lg font-bold text-[var(--color-text-primary)] mb-3" style="font-family: var(--font-display);">5. Children</h2>
        <p>GoinAtlas is not directed at children under 13. We do not knowingly collect data from children.</p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-lg font-bold text-[var(--color-text-primary)] mb-3" style="font-family: var(--font-display);">6. Changes</h2>
        <p>We may update this policy. Changes are posted on this page with a revised date.</p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-lg font-bold text-[var(--color-text-primary)] mb-3" style="font-family: var(--font-display);">7. Contact</h2>
        <p>Questions about this policy: <a href="mailto:hello@goinatlas.com" class="text-[var(--color-brand-600)] hover:underline">hello@goinatlas.com</a></p>
      </section>

    </div>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
